    "body": "Fixes #5397\r\nFixes #13398\r\n\r\nAt some point, the options for the gcc package to rpath it's dependencies properly during the bootstrap phase got moved into a conditional that only runs when building `gcc+binutils`. This caused `gcc~binutils` to fail when `target=aarch64:`.\r\n\r\nThis PR moves that logic out of the conditional.\r\n",
